name: Fedora Gold
description: Fedora Gold FED coin is a CryptoNote based privacy coin backed by a strong project team with a growing community of active users. The Fedora network is secure and extremely fast (transactions resolve under 5 seconds). Our vision is to build a privacy based coin solution that works on any standard mobile device. Our use cases are: - Instant & private transactions - Usable by anyone, anywhere - Social interaction and commerce
